# Treadstone 71 Executive Decision Support Templates

Corporate leaders demand actionable intelligence. Security centers frequently deliver unstructured data dumps. Analysts must transform raw indicators into defensible boardroom strategy. We built the adaptive cyber intelligence lifecycle to bridge the gap between technical observation and executive action.

Providing an empty template forces the operator to recognize analytical blind spots. You must apply advanced intel analysis ai methods to complete the brief. 

## The T71 Standard

Standard reports fail because authors mix verified facts with adversary claims. We mandate the use of standard words of estimative probability (Sherman Kent style) for all forecasts. 

*   Highly Likely (85-95%)
*   Probable / Likely (60-80%)
*   Even Chance (45-55%)
*   Unlikely (20-40%)

## Immediate Action

Download the `T71_Strategic_Brief.md` template. Use the document to structure your next executive update. Ensure you rank evidence and mark all analytical uncertainty. 

